<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>BFC的区域不会与float box重叠。</title>
    <style>
        body {
            width: 600px;
            position: relative;
            background-color: #0082CB;
        }

        .aside {
            width: 200px;
            height:200px;
            float: left;
            background: red;
        }

        .main {
            height: 500px;
            background: green;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="aside"></div>
<div class="main"></div>
</body>
</html>